{"tha-ap473:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap473:0.2":"Nalamalivagga ","tha-ap473:0.3":"Nalamaliyattheraapadana ","tha-ap473:1.1":"“Suvannavannam sambuddham, ","tha-ap473:1.2":"Ahutinam patiggaham; ","tha-ap473:1.3":"Vipinaggena gacchantam, ","tha-ap473:1.4":"Addasam lokanayakam. ","tha-ap473:2.1":"Nalamalam gahetvana, ","tha-ap473:2.2":"nikkhamanto ca tavade; ","tha-ap473:2.3":"Tatthaddasasim sambuddham, ","tha-ap473:2.4":"oghatinnamanasavam. ","tha-ap473:3.1":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap473:3.2":"nalamalamapujayim; ","tha-ap473:3.3":"Dakkhineyyam mahaviram, ","tha-ap473:3.4":"sabbalokanukampakam. ","tha-ap473:4.1":"Ekatimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap473:4.2":"yam malamabhiropayim; ","tha-ap473:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap473:4.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap473:5.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap473:5.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap473:5.3":"Nagova bandhanam chetva, ","tha-ap473:5.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap473:6.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap473:6.2":"mama buddhassa santike; ","tha-ap473:6.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","tha-ap473:6.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap473:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap473:7.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap473:7.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap473:7.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap473:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma nalamaliyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap473:9.1":"Nalamaliyattherassapadanam pathamam. "}